name: Jesse Llama - Remedy Parody #4
description: Jesse Llama thought she just scored the government research job of her life, until she realized things are not as they seem at the FBC. A plague of strange mind controlling sound has caused the entire mysterious building to go on lockdown, and Jesse Llama has to fix it (of course while she can't escape). Thankfully this llama got special powers, so of course she can save the day with ease... and an aimbot because of the poor optimization :')
